In [16]:
bggclf=BaggingClassifier(DecisionTreeClassifier(),
                        n_estimators=100,max_samples=25,bootstrap=True,
                        n_jobs=-1)
bggclf.fit(x_train,y_train)
y_pred=bggclf.predict(x_test)
acc=accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred)
x_min,x_max=x_train[:,0].min()-1,x_train[:,0].max()+1
y_min,y_max =x_train[:,1].min()-1,x_train[:, 1].max()+1
xx,yy=np.meshgrid(np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1),
                     np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1))
z=bggclf.predict(np.c_[xx.ravel(),yy.ravel()])
z=z.reshape(xx.shape)
plt.contourf(xx,yy,z,alpha=0.4)
plt.scatter(x[:,0],x[:,1],c=y,s=20,edgecolor='k')
plt.title(f"accuracy is {round(acc,4)}")
plt.show()
In [17]:
n_est=[5,10,25,50,100,250,500]
for i in n_est:
    bggclf=BaggingClassifier(DecisionTreeClassifier(),
                        n_estimators=i,max_samples=24,bootstrap=True,
                        n_jobs=-1)
    bggclf.fit(x_train,y_train)
    y_pred=bggclf.predict(x_test)
    acc=accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred)
    x_min,x_max=x_train[:,0].min()-1,x_train[:,0].max()+1
    y_min,y_max =x_train[:,1].min()-1,x_train[:, 1].max()+1
    xx,yy=np.meshgrid(np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1),
                     np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1))
    z=bggclf.predict(np.c_[xx.ravel(),yy.ravel()])
    z=z.reshape(xx.shape)
    plt.contourf(xx,yy,z,alpha=0.4)
    plt.scatter(x[:,0],x[:,1],c=y,s=20,edgecolor='k')
    plt.title(f"Bagging , n_estimators is {i} accuracy is {round(acc,4)}")
    plt.show()

max_sam=[2,5,10,15,20,25,30,40,50]
for i in max_sam:
    bggclf=BaggingClassifier(DecisionTreeClassifier(),
                        n_estimators=100,max_samples=i,bootstrap=False,
                        n_jobs=-1)
    bggclf.fit(x_train,y_train)
    y_pred=bggclf.predict(x_test)
    acc=accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred)
    x_min,x_max=x_train[:,0].min()-1,x_train[:,0].max()+1
    y_min,y_max =x_train[:,1].min()-1,x_train[:, 1].max()+1
    xx,yy=np.meshgrid(np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1),
                     np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1))
    z=bggclf.predict(np.c_[xx.ravel(),yy.ravel()])
    z=z.reshape(xx.shape)
    plt.contourf(xx,yy,z,alpha=0.4)
    plt.scatter(x[:,0],x[:,1],c=y,s=20,edgecolor='k')
    plt.title(f"pasting , max_samples is {i} accuracy is {round(acc,4)}")
    plt.show()

Decision trees¶

In [21]:
for i in range(1,15):
    estimator=DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=i)
    estimator.fit(x_train,y_train)
    y_pred=estimator.predict(x_test)
    acc=accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred)
    x_min,x_max=x[:,0].min()-1,x[:,0].max()+1
    y_min,y_max =x[:,1].min()-1,x[:, 1].max()+1
    xx,yy=np.meshgrid(np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1),
                     np.arange(x_min,x_max,0.1))
    z=estimator.predict(np.c_[xx.ravel(),yy.ravel()])
    z=z.reshape(xx.shape)
    plt.contourf(xx,yy,z,alpha=0.4)
    plt.scatter(x[:,0],x[:,1],c=y,s=20,edgecolor='k')
    plt.title(f"max depth is {i} and accuracy is {round(acc,4)}")
    plt.show()
